{"tid":1503831,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"連續2日停公共交通 香港係咪戒嚴？","createTime":"2019-08-25T05:54:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-26T13:45:59.000Z","uid":79085,"like":94,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"8ce97e0f37852cfd790aa3bce6f2baaef5fc0509","tid":1503831,"uid":79085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T05:54:05.000Z","msg":"1956年雙十暴動中，時任輔政司、署理香港總督戴維德決定當日下午7時30分至10月12日上午10時在<span style=\"color: red;\">九龍</span>實施<span style=\"color: red;\">戒嚴</span>，期間所有公共交通停止服務，渡海小輪及九廣鐵路英段（今港鐵東鐵線）停駛，部分<span style=\"color: red;\">公共服務停頓</span>，其後將戒嚴延令至10月14日上午10時。<br />\n<br />\n而家已經連續2日停公共交通，報案室同好多政府機構暫停服務，警隊又入屋苑清場放催淚彈，係街又無差別對路人返工放工照清場，街燈又可以熄。其實係咪已經戒嚴緊?"},{"pid":"00c486a47cbeb24bd34dad22d4289f4afb0bacfb","tid":1503831,"uid":110509,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T05:55:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">9月1 (日) 一定係機場</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">9月14中秋,未必CALL 到人, 所以</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">9月7 (六), 9 月8(日) 連續2日一定係機場</span></span> <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">全部1點，唯一底線，唔衝禁區(會變恐襲)</span></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">之後既每個星期六/日 要起碼有一日一定係機場，<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">乜撚都要讓路!!</span></span></span><br />\n<br />\n聽日826 仲有國泰城<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3f44de0dd9329e3af26dd01ccbf5020706bbb46","tid":1503831,"uid":298664,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"8ce97e0f37852cfd790aa3bce6f2baaef5fc0509","tid":1503831,"uid":79085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T05:54:05.000Z","msg":"1956年雙十暴動中，時任輔政司、署理香港總督戴維德決定當日下午7時30分至10月12日上午10時在<span style=\"color: red;\">九龍</span>實施<span style=\"color: red;\">戒嚴</span>，期間所有公共交通停止服務，渡海小輪及九廣鐵路英段（今港鐵東鐵線）停駛，部分<span style=\"color: red;\">公共服務停頓</span>，其後將戒嚴延令至10月14日上午10時。<br />\n<br />\n而家已經連續2日停公共交通，報案室同好多政府機構暫停服務，警隊又入屋苑清場放催淚彈，係街又無差別對路人返工放工照清場，街燈又可以熄。其實係咪已經戒嚴緊?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T05:55:42.000Z","msg":"借位<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tW3cYUK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtW3cYUK.jpg&h=7136da62&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1c624b909c8418568790f7fcec6861ddf8510951","tid":1503831,"uid":79085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T05:57:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0de6ba8df7aa12137d97061f590eed532c79bc32","tid":1503831,"uid":79085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T06:01:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"624a65b156cdcaad3d5442f4c8a09db877e073ea","tid":1503831,"uid":230890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T06:03:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8f76e3a8b9ab824caf1f32dba43778181d769926","tid":1503831,"uid":230890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T06:03:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ebc0570dc63520cfadf5186f32f44051d9dd42c5","tid":1503831,"uid":103363,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T06:05:01.000Z","msg":"係戒嚴緊，文宣可以講多D"},{"pid":"5b08831c19cf7ab775ed45a5b2e88cd557c34be9","tid":1503831,"uid":279253,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T06:05:25.000Z","msg":"根本變相宵禁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲要係日光白白都禁"},{"pid":"a70573ac1197128dc531dc7796515497f25330fe","tid":1503831,"uid":79085,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T06:06:39.000Z","msg":"雙十暴動，期間公共交通停止服務<br />\n<br />\n今日，港鐵荃葵青遊行前封3站 防暴警葵芳站驅散市民"},{"pid":"84a7880dc457b9a68ad3db8c35c14290d841a758","tid":1503831,"uid":269578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T06:06:57.000Z","msg":"係"},{"pid":"edace8b65e7cb92f44b5b9a50c124412a357029a","tid":1503831,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2